This guide will help you add DNS Records to your DNS Zone hosted as DNS Zone.

## Requirements
To be able to add DNS records you have to first [create](/tutorials/partner-portal/domains/dns-setting-up-production-domain) and [configure](/tutorials/partner-portal/domains/dns-setting-up-production-domain-pos) the Domain as a DNS Zone.

